dadamachines TBD App Template

The official starting point for building RP2350 apps for the dadamachines
TBD-16 audio DSP platform.

This repository is maintained by dadamachines and originated from the
RP2350 firmware template developed by Robert Manzke at the Creative
Technologies Arbeitsgruppe of Kiel University of Applied Sciences:
https://www.creative-technologies.de

(c) 2024-2026 Robert Manzke. All rights reserved. (Original RP2350 firmware template and SPI API)
(c) 2024-2026 Johannes Elias Lohbihler for dadamachines. (App template adaptation, documentation)


