YOUR APP CODE
-------------

The code you write in your app (e.g. your main.cpp, your custom UI logic,
your sequencer, your effects controller) is YOUR code under YOUR license.

The LGPL applies only to the template libraries provided in this repository
(src/SpiAPI, src/Midi, src/MidiParser, src/Ui, and related headers). If you
modify those libraries and distribute the result, share the modifications
under LGPL 3.0.


THE DADAMACHINES NAME AND BRAND
-------------------------------
The dadamachines name, logo, and TBD-16 product name are trademarks of
dadamachines and are reserved for products produced by or licensed by
dadamachines.

If you build a product or app using the TBD platform, you may reference it as:
  - [YourApp] for TBD
  - [YourApp] (TBD-compatible)

Using "dadamachines [YourApp]" or "TBD-16 [YourApp]" is not permitted
without prior agreement.


COMMERCIAL USE
--------------
If you want to build a commercial product around the TBD platform:

  - TBD-Core: Our core DSP board with all audio, MIDI, and USB I/O
    assembled. Connect your own UI board via the 30-pin FFC connector
    and design your own enclosure.
  - Custom Integration: We integrate the ESP32-P4, RP2350, and codec
    directly onto your PCB for full control over form factor, connectors,
    and BOM.

See https://dadamachines.com/contact/ for details.

If you modify the template libraries and distribute them, those
modifications must be released under LGPL 3.0. If you would like to keep
your modifications proprietary, dadamachines can provide a commercial
license. Contact us: https://dadamachines.com/contact/


HARDWARE DESIGNS
----------------
The dadamachines TBD-16 (desktop instrument) and TBD-Core (core DSP board
for custom products) are commercial products. Their hardware designs are
proprietary and not released under an open-source license.

An open-hardware core design based on the same ESP32-P4 + RP2350 platform
is planned for future publication in KiCad as an open-source reference,
to foster education, prototyping, and instrument design.


